        "text": "فَٱذْكُرُونِىٓ أَذْكُرْكُمْ وَٱشْكُرُوا۟ لِى وَلَا تَكْفُرُونِ",
        "translationEn": "So remember Me; I will remember you. And be grateful to Me and do not deny Me.",
